I'm afraid, Simone.

1333
02:02:29,377 --> 02:02:32,337
I'm losing my memory. It's very serious.

1334
02:02:34,257 --> 02:02:36,133
My thoughts are muddled.

1335
02:02:37,177 --> 02:02:39,845
I'm trying to remember...

1336
02:02:40,722 --> 02:02:42,264
but I can't.

1337
02:02:44,100 --> 02:02:48,061
Other memories are surfacing,
not the ones I want to see.

1338
